<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.3.9">
<l>meytimirum nāṉap poṭiyōṭu mañcaḷum</l>
<l>ceyya taṭaṅkaṇṇuk kañcaṉamum cinturamum</l>
<l>veyya kalaippāki koṇṭu vaḷāyniṉṟā</l>
<l>ḷaiyā vaḻēlaḻēl tālēlō varaṅkat taṇaiyāṉē tālēlō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The female rider of the fierce stag stood nearby holding vermilion,</l>
<l>kajal for [your] red, wide eyes,</l>
<l>and tumeric with fragrant powder that is rubbed on [your] body.</l>
<l>Master, do not cry, do not cry, tālēlō! You who recline in Araṅkam, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
